<LP>
   SACRAMENTO, Calif. -- McLaren Environmental Engineering
Inc., a unit of Sandoz International Ltd.'s Sandoz Corp.
affiliate, said it changed its name to McLaren/ Hart after
acquiring Hart Environmental Management Corp., New York.
Terms of the acquisition weren't disclosed. McLaren said the
transaction created one of the largest firms in the U.S. for
environmental engineering and management.
